You've built a solid SQL foundation that will serve you well in your transition to data analytics. You now know how to:

Query databases with SELECT, FROM, LIMIT, and ORDER BY
Find unique values with DISTINCT
Create professional aliases with AS
Understand how databases and SQL clients work together
This is a major step forward in your journey toward becoming a data analyst. Keep practicing these skills, and you'll be writing powerful queries in no time!


